Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, dear brothers and sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so happy to share with you this update.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been amazing\Nto see the Kingdom work move ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,even during this pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Various branches are reporting all-time peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in the number of publishers, pioneers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting attendance, and Bible studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Many have reported peaks\Nin the Memorial attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nthe Philippines branch reported
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that over 739,000
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,attended the Memorial this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That is more than three times\Nthe number of publishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred congregations,\Nmostly in urban areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,reported a Memorial attendance\Nof at least 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:01:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that 50,000 attended the Memorial
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in just those 100 congregations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In various parts of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,many struggle to obtain food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With the assistance of hundreds\Nof Disaster Relief Committees,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we continue to help our brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nin Venezuela, each month,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we are providing\Nan average of 130 tons of food
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to 25,000 brothers in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One 90-year-old pioneer sister said:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“I know that the aid comes from Jehovah,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,“but he uses brothers\Nthat I do not even know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“and yet they love me and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear family.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It is heartwarming\Nto see how Jehovah is helping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,our brothers and sisters in Venezuela\Nand around the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank all of you for making that possible
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,by means of your donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In our last {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}Governing Body Update,{
}\NBrother Herd mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that “about 50 percent\Nof the worldwide Bethel family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,have been vaccinated so far.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Initially, it seemed impossible\Nto obtain vaccines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in some countries of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has been amazing to see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that now more than 80 percent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of our worldwide Bethel family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,—that is, more than 19,000 Bethelites—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are vaccinated,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are doing what we can\Nto assist the branch offices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that have not been able to obtain vaccines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know,\Nby keeping the Bethel family safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we protect the flow of spiritual food
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and support spiritual activities worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of the Governing Body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you, dear brothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for your tremendous cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the arrangements\Nduring the pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been many adjustments\Nin a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have done so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We truly love you for your fine spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in working “shoulder to shoulder” with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,While we all have had changes in our routine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,some of our circuit overseers\Nwho serve in foreign lands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have had major changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to return to their home countries\Nduring the pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, some continue to serve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the congregations in their circuits via Zoom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,despite being in a different country
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and in a different time zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hear from one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A few months into the pandemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my father’s health was failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we made the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to the States
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and assist my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Although in the beginning\Nwe didn’t think we’d be here so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it turned out that the surge in the pandemic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,prevented us from going back\Nto our assignment in the circuit in Bolivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being displaced,\Nwe just weren’t sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if we were going to be able to serve\Nand complete our assignment effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We felt that we needed to make
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the necessary adjustments\Nto have the right attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So fervent prayer really helped us\Nto get the right mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And being able to see\Nhow Jehovah answered those prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is very faith-strengthening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah is blessing this arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the arrangement\Nthat has been put in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and it’s what we’re using.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re making the best of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But we’re having success\Nbecause Jehovah is behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve had brothers who are now qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to be publishers\N—unbaptized publishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There are brothers\Nwho’ve dedicated their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and gotten baptized during this pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One brother in particular\Nhas so much enthusiasm for phone witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that last month he was able\Nto report over 100 return visits,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was able to show\Nover 200 videos to different ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One Bible student loves her study so much,\Nand also attending meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that she’s willing to walk one hour each way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to have a good signal on her phone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so that she can tie in to her study\Nand also to the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout this past year,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve learned that Jehovah has never left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s been in total control\Nof every situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s been able to direct\Nhis organization, his people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly to the place that we need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This has all been proof\Nthat Jehovah will never abandon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How encouraging to hear how our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are remaining united and spiritually active!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do have to continue\Nto guard our unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is unity?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been defined as “oneness,”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“a condition of harmony.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Note how the apostle Paul describes our role
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in maintaining unity at Ephesians 4:3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There we read:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,“earnestly endeavoring to maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“the oneness of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in the uniting bond of peace.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Note that it takes effort\Nto maintain our unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul said that we must “earnestly endeavor,”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or work hard, at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What could pose a danger to our unity?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we\Nbecame too emotionally involved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in issues that are divisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bible foretold at 2 Timothy chapter 3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that men would be “lovers of themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,“. . . not open to any agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,. . . [and] fierce.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We see this in the world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People are “not open to any agreement.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They quickly become “fierce,”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,taking strong positions\Non all types of issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As Christians,\Nwe are “no part of [the] world.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We stay out of those debates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nwho would have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that wearing a mask\Nto prevent the spread of disease
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,could become an issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From the time when we were little children,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,our parents taught us to cover our mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when we coughed or sneezed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In his precious Word,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah outlined many practical measures
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that would prevent the spread of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So how could wearing a mask\Nbecome controversial for some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that thinking coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us are exposed to worldly thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,on television, on the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at work, or at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many websites\Nthat promote conspiracy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we’re not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we could become emotionally involved\Nin these debates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We could allow ourselves to be guided\Nby “the voice of strangers”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of listening to Jehovah’s channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“the faithful and discreet slave.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As we face the end of this system of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this will become more and more essential
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to our safety and spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why we appreciate\Nyou dear brothers and sisters so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you discern that Jehovah’s spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is directing the Governing Body\Nto go in a certain way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you are quick to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result, we enjoy precious unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me\Nof the Bible example of Naaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Through a messenger,\Nthe prophet Elisha told Naaman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,he would be healed from his leprosy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,if he bathed seven times in the Jordan River.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Naaman react?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s read together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,2 Kings 5:11, 12:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“At this Naaman became indignant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“and started to leave, saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘Here I said to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘“He will come out to me and stand here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘“and call on the name of Jehovah his God,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘“moving his hand back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘over the leprosy to cure it.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘Are not the Abanah and the Pharpar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘the rivers of Damascus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘better than all the waters of Israel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“Can I not wash in them and become clean?’
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With that he turned and went away in a rage.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Naaman had his own idea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about how he was going to be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt strongly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jehovah had a different idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To be cured,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Naaman would have to humble himself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and follow direction from Jehovah’s channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naaman was struggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but his servants got the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they tell him to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s read verses 13 and 14:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“His servants now approached him and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘My father, if the prophet had told you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘to do something extraordinary,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘would you not do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,“‘How much more, then, since he
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“only said to you, “Wash and be clean”?’
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“At that he went down
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,“and plunged into the Jordan seven times,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,“according to the word
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“of the man of the true God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,“Then his flesh was restored
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“like the flesh of a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and he became clean.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we get the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Naaman,\Nwe might struggle a bit at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,especially if we have\Nour own strong viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But one thing is certain:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we follow direction\Ncoming from Jehovah’s channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be blessed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and, more important,\Nwe will remain united.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Devil is not happy\Nto see this cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,—this beautiful unity that we enjoy—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to be on guard\Nso as to maintain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of an event in my life,\Nmany years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when this lesson was impressed on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time,\Nsome of the brothers did become divided
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it led to so many problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You may remember
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that we had a video about those events.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s watch a clip from that video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of pressure was\Non the brothers in Romania.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Communist Party tried
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to sow distrust among the brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting with them separately
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and telling some brothers one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and telling other brothers something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it happened
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that an official posed\Nas an interested person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and was clever enough to disguise that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretend to make progress in the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,—not only to the point of getting baptized
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but even to the point of becoming an elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was in reality\Nan agent of the secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with an aim to find out everything\Nabout the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it did lead to, in one case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the brothers starting to distrust someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that was actually appointed by headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And these brothers then separated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from the organization that Jehovah used,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of them were separated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for not just a few years but for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were a large number,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,up to 5,000 publishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They continued to meet together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They were preaching and using material\Nthat they had left over from earlier years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but they hardly got any new material to study
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were not in touch\Nwith the organization
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that was used by headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempts to bring the brothers back\Ninto the organization
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,were made from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seemed that the brothers\Nfrom the separated organization
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,did not have sufficient trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we presented
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the leader of the separated group
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that one from the Governing Body would come,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he was happy about that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and he had enough trust in that case
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to agree that we should have a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and seriously talk about reunification.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And so from the separated group,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there were Brother Albu, who was the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and four of his main elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And from our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there was Brother Jaracz, our translator,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was part of that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there were
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,several from the Country Committee of Romania.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that the first night
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there were a lot of accusations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about what the others had done or not done,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which did not create the best spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we mainly listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But everybody agreed to meet another night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second night,\NJehovah obviously wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the brothers to unite again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because the whole spirit was different,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the brothers talked the matters over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and clarified some misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of the second evening,\NI remember
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that the leader of the separated group,\NBrother Albu, said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‘Let’s do it because if we don’t do it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we may never have another opportunity again.’
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the decision was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t happen every day\Nthat 5,000 brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,come back to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on,\Nall the practical things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,were put in place\Nto accomplish this reunification.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They were asked to merge\Nwith our congregations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that also took\Na lot of humility on their part,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were willing to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So they were really brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in their heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and loved the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the reunification was accomplished,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was a wonderful victory for Jehovah\Nand against Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflecting on the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with the brothers in Romania,\Nwe can see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that there could always be\Nmisunderstandings among humans
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and there could always be\Neven legitimate complaints
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about the misconduct\Nof some responsible brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the important thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,never to lose trust\Nthat this is Jehovah’s organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s where Jehovah’s blessing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah sees it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah uses his holy spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep the organization together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and what he wants to have accomplished\Nwill happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work with the holy spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then Jehovah will bless our efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will be successful to his praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nthese challenges were not unique
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to the brothers in Romania.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Similar challenges\Noccurred in other countries
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that were behind the Iron Curtain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,including Czechoslovakia,\NRussia, and Ukraine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what have we learned in this update?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah’s organization is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even during this pandemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we see strong evidence\Nthat Jehovah’s spirit is blessing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and moving ahead\Nthe preaching and disciple-making work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite many challenges,\Nyou dear brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,are working hard\Nto maintain our precious unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result,\Nwe are enjoying a spiritual paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as we work unitedly together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan will continue to try\Nto stir up division,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even among Jehovah’s people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do\Nto successfully resist his efforts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to the channel that Jehovah is using,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,“the faithful and discreet slave.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t allow yourself\Nto become emotionally involved
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with the causes of this world,\Nwhatever they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt\Nthat Jehovah will richly bless
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all those who support our King, Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the channel that he is using today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,“the faithful and discreet slave.”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From the World Headquarters\Nof Jehovah’s Witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,this is JW Broadcasting®.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:04.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,愛する兄弟姉妹 ようこそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:07.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんにお話しできることを\Nうれしく思います
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,このパンデミック中も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:14.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,王国の活動が前進しているのは\N素晴らしいことです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:20.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,多くの支部は\N伝道者の最高数を報告しています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:26.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,開拓者 集会出席者\N聖書レッスンの数についても同様です
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:31.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,記念式の出席者が最高数になった国も\Nたくさんあります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:35.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,例えば フィリピン支部の報告によると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:41.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,今年の記念式に73万9000人以上が\N出席しました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:46.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,これは 伝道者数の3倍以上に当たります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:52.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,100の会衆では\N主に都市部にある会衆ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:56.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,記念式にそれぞれ500人以上が\N出席しました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから この100の会衆だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:03.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,5万人以上が記念式に\N出席したことになります
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:10.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,多くの国では 食べ物を手に入れることが\N困難になっています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:15.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちは 各地の災害救援\N委員会を通して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:18.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうした地域の兄弟姉妹を\N援助しています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:27.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,例えば ベネズエラでは\N毎月平均130トンの食料を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:31.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,2万5000人の困窮した兄弟姉妹に\N届けています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,90歳の開拓者の姉妹は\Nこう言っています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,「助けてくださっているエホバに\N感謝しています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは 会ったこともない兄弟たちを\N通して助けてくれています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちは親身になって\N援助してくれます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:51.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟姉妹 本当にありがとうございます」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:59.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,うれしいことに エホバは\Nベネズエラの兄弟姉妹を助けています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,世界各地の兄弟姉妹のこともです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:08.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうした援助ができるのは\N皆さんの惜しみない寄付のおかげです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,前回の「統治体からの話」で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,ハード兄弟は その時までに\N「世界中のベテル家族の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:20.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,約50パーセントがワクチンの接種を\N終え」たと述べていました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:28.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,当初 ある国々ではワクチンを\N入手することが不可能に思えました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:35.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも驚くべきことに 今では\N世界中のベテル家族の80パーセント以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:43.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,つまり1万9000人以上のベテル奉仕者が\Nワクチンの接種を終えています
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちは まだワクチンを\N入手できていない支部事務所を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,援助するため ベストを尽くしています
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:55.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,ベテル家族の安全を\N確保することによって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:59.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,信仰を強める食物が\N途絶えることなく供給され
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:02.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,世界中の活動をサポートする\Nことができています
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:10.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,パンデミック中 全ての取り決めに\N快く協力してくださっている兄弟姉妹に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:14.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,統治体を代表して\N心からの感謝をお伝えします
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,短い期間にさまざまな\N調整がありましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当によく協力してくださいました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんを心から愛しています
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:30.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんは私たちと「肩を並べて」\N働いてくださっています
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちの生活は\Nいろいろな面で変化しました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:42.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,特に大きな変化を経験したのは\N外国で奉仕している巡回監督です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:47.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,パンデミック中 故国に\N帰らなければならなかった人もいます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,それでもZoomを通して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:54.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,割り当てられた巡回区で\N引き続き奉仕している人たちもいます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:59.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,国境や時差を越えて\N奉仕を続けています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,1組の夫婦にお聞きしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:09.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,パンデミックになって間もなく\N父の健康状態が悪化しました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:14.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,それで 母をサポートするため\N米国に戻ることにしました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:20.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,最初は 米国での滞在がこれほど長くなる\Nとは思っていませんでしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,パンデミックのせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,ボリビアの巡回区に戻ることが\Nできませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,ボリビアに戻れない状態で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:32.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,巡回区での奉仕をきちんと行えるのか\N正直不安でした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:37.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,必要な調整を行って 正しい見方を\N持てるようにする必要があると思いました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:42.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,正しい考え方をするために\N熱烈な祈りが助けになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが私の祈りを\Nよく聞いてくださったので
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当に信仰が強まりました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの祝福を感じています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:55.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,組織がこういう取り決めを\N設けてくれたので 十分に活用しています
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:59.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも うまくいっているのは\Nエホバのおかげです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:04.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,パンデミック中に進歩して 伝道者になる\N資格を身に付けた人たちもいます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:08.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,中には 献身して\Nバプテスマを受けた人たちもいます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:14.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,ある兄弟は 電話伝道を\Nとても熱心に行っています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:17.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,先月 再訪問を100件以上行い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:22.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,いろいろな人に200回以上\Nビデオを見せることができました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:28.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,ある女性は 聖書をとても熱心に学び\N集会にも出席しています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書レッスンをしたり\N集会に出席したりするために
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:36.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,電波のよく入る所まで\N1時間もかけて歩いていっています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:42.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,過去1年 エホバは決して\N私たちを見捨てたりしませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,全ての状況を完全に把握しています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:51.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは ご自分の民や組織が\N何をすべきかを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,はっきりと教えてくれています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが私たちを\N決して見捨てたりしないことの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:57.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,強力な証拠です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当に励まされます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,このような状況の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:08.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちは一致して\N熱心に活動しています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:12.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちはこの一致を守りたいと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,一致とは何ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:20.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,「一つであること」とか\N「調和した状態」と定義されています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,一致を保つため\N私たちは何をしなければなりませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,パウロがエフェソス 4:3で\N述べていることに注目しましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうあります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,「平和という絆で結ばれ，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:40.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖なる力による一致を保つよう\N真剣に努力してください」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,一致というのは\N努力して保つ必要があります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:50.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,パウロが述べた通り\N「真剣に努力」する必要があるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:56.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,どんなものが\N一致を脅かす恐れがありますか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,賛否両論のある問題に\Nあまりにも深入りするなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,どうなるでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:09.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,テモテ第二 3章では 人々が\N「自分を愛し⋯⋯全く人に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:14.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,同意しようとせず⋯⋯乱暴」に\Nなることが予告されていました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,今の世界はまさにそうなっています
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,人々は「全く⋯⋯同意しようと\N［しません］」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,すぐに「乱暴」になります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,いろいろな問題について\N強い意見を主張します
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちクリスチャンは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:34.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,「この世界のものでは［ない］」ので\Nそういう議論に関わりません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:42.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,例えば私たちは 感染を防ぐために\Nマスクをすることが議論になるなどとは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,考えもしませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:49.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちが子供の頃から親は\Nせきやくしゃみをするときには
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,口を覆うように と教えてくれました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:08:00.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書にも 病気が広がるのを防ぐための\Nさまざまな予防策が記されています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,では マスクをするかどうかが\N問題になるのはなぜですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,そういう考えは\Nどこから来ているのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちは注意しなければなりません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:20.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,テレビや インターネットや 職場や 学校で\N世の考え方にさらされているからです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:25.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,陰謀論を広めるウェブサイトも\Nたくさんあります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,注意しないと 私たちもそうした情報に\N振り回されてしまうかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:38.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちは 「知らない人⋯⋯の声」ではなく\Nエホバが用いている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:42.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,「忠実で思慮深い奴隷」に\N従う必要があります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:48.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,このことは 終わりが近い今 特に重要です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:52.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバとの絆を保ち\N間違った情報に惑わされないためです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:58.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,この点で私たちは\N兄弟姉妹に深く感謝しています
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんはエホバの聖なる力が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:08.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,統治体をある方向に導いていることに\N気付くとすぐに それに従っています
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:13.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,その結果 私たちは一致していられます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書に記されている\Nナアマンの例を思い出します
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,預言者エリシャは 使者を通して\Nナアマンにこう伝えました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:29.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,「ヨルダン川で7回体を洗えば\N重い皮膚病が治ります」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,ナアマンはどうするでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:39.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,ご一緒に 列王第二 5:11, 12を\N読んでみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:46.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,「するとナアマンは憤慨し\N立ち去ろうとして言った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:52.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,『私は 「彼が私の所に出てきてここに立ち\N彼の神エホバの名を呼んで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:57.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,手を患部の上で前後に動かして\N治すのだろう」と思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,ダマスカスのアバナ川や
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:04.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,ファルパル川の方が イスラエルの\Nどの川よりもいいではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,それらの川で体を洗うのでは\N清くなれないのか』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうして彼は向きを変え\N怒りながら去っていった」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:16.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,ナアマンは エリシャが\Nどのように病気を治すのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:20.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,勝手なイメージを持っていました\N強く思い込んでいたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも エホバの考えは違いました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,ナアマンは治してもらうために
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,謙遜になって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの預言者の指示に\N従わなければなりませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:37.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,ナアマンは従おうとはしませんでしたが\N家来たちは違いました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,ナアマンに何と言いましたか\Nどんな結果になったでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,13, 14節を読んでみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,「すると家来たちが\Nナアマンに近寄ってこう言った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,『ご主人さま あの預言者から
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,何か大変なことをするように\N言われたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,その通りになさるのではありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:02.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼はただ 「体を洗って 清くなりなさい」\Nと言ったのですから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:07.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうしてもよいのではありませんか』\Nそれでナアマンは行って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:13.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,真の神に遣わされた人に言われた通り\Nヨルダン川に７回体を浸した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:20.67,Default2,,0,0,0,,すると 彼の肌は元に戻って\N少年の肌のようになり 清くなった」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,何を学べますか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:28.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちも指示に従いにくく\N感じることがあるかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,強い意見を持っているときは\N特にそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも確かなことがあります
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:39.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが用いている人たちの指示に\N従うなら 祝福され
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:43.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,さらに大切なこととして\N一致していられるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:48.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,もちろん悪魔は このことを\Nうれしく思っていません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:52.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,私たちが一致しているのが\N気に入らないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:56.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから 一致を守るために\N努力しなければなりません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:00.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん前のことになりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:04.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,この一致を守ることに関して\N忘れられない経験があります
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,当時 一部の兄弟たちが\N組織を離れてしまったため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,さまざまな問題が生じました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:17.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,その出来事を取り上げたビデオを\N覚えておられるかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,その一部を見てみましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:27.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,状況が特に難しかったのは\Nルーマニアです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:32.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,共産党は兄弟たちの間に\N不信の種をまこうとしました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,別々に兄弟たちに会い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,一方にはあることを伝え
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:40.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,他方にはまた違うことを伝えました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:46.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,時には当局者が真理に\N関心がある人のふりをし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:51.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちをだまして\N進歩しているかのように見せました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,バプテスマを受けただけでなく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:56.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,長老にさえなった人もいます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:13:02.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも実際は 組織の全体を\N探り出すことを目的とした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,秘密警察の工作員だったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,その影響で ある兄弟たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,本部によって任命された兄弟に\N対する不信感を募らせていき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:21.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,結果として エホバが用いておられる\N組織から離れていきました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:25.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,ある人たちは数年はおろか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,何十年も離れてしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうした人たちは大勢いて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,5000人ほどもいました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,その人たちも集まり続け
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,伝道もしていましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:44.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,以前から持っていた資料\Nだけでそうしていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:50.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,本部が用いる組織とは\N接触を断っていたので
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,新しい研究用の資料は何も\N手に入れられませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:01.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,離れた人たちが組織に\N戻れるようにする試みは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,度々行なわれましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:08.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らはまだ兄弟たちを十分に\N信頼していないようでした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:12.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかし 離れたグループのリーダーに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,統治体の成員の一人が\N来ることを伝えると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,それなら信頼できるということで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちが再び1つになるための
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:26.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,真剣な話し合いを持つ\Nことに喜んで応じました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,離れたグループからは\Nリーダーであるアルブ兄弟と
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,主だった長老たち4人が参加しました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:41.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしたちの側は\Nジャラズ兄弟と通訳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:48.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたし そしてルーマニアの国内\N委員会の代表者たちがいました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:57.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,最初の日の夜 彼らは兄弟たちに\N対する非難をたくさん述べました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:03.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,険悪な雰囲気でしたが\Nわたしたちは耳を傾けました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:10.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 別の夜に会合を持つこと\Nにはみな同意しました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:14.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,2日目の夜 エホバが彼らに\N戻って来て欲しいと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,願っておられることが\N明らかになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らの態度が全く変わっており
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,全てを話して誤解を解いたからです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:30.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,その日の終わり アルブ兄弟が\Nこう言ったのを今でも覚えています
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,「もう一度１つになろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,いま組織に戻らなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,二度とチャンスはないかもしれない」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうして戻ることを決定したのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:51.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,1日で5000人の兄弟たちが\N組織に戻ってくるなんて･･･
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,その時から 再び1つになるために
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,全てのことが組織されました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:05.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らにはわたしたちの会衆に\N加わることが求められました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,それはとても謙遜さがいることでしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:12.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼らは喜んでそうしました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:16.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,兄弟たちは本当に誠実であり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,真理を愛していたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:23.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうして兄弟たちは再び1つになり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:29.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,これはサタンに対するエホバの\N素晴らしい勝利となりました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:34.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,ルーマニアの兄弟たちの\N経験を振り返ると
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:40.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,不完全な人間の間では常に\N誤解が生じ得ることや
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:43.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,責任を担っている\N兄弟たちの間違いによって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:48.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,正当な不満さえ抱きかねない\Nことがよく分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:50.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも大切なのは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,これがエホバの組織であることへの\N信頼を決して失わないことです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが祝福しておられる組織です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,全てをご覧になっています
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:06.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバは聖霊を用いて\N組織を一致させておられ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:09.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,望むことを成し遂げられる方です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:13.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,わたしたちが聖霊と共に働くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:17.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバはその努力を祝福して成功させ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:26.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,こうしてエホバに賛美が\Nもたらされるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,このような問題を経験したのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,ルーマニアの兄弟たち\Nだけではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,同じようなことが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,鉄のカーテンの向こうの\N他の国々でも起きていました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:43.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,チェコスロバキア ロシア\Nウクライナなどです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:49.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんは この話から何を学びましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの組織は 今も前進しています
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,このパンデミック中も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:59.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,良い知らせを伝え\N人々を弟子とする活動を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが祝福し\N前進させていることは明らかです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:13.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,皆さんはさまざまな問題と闘いながら\N一致を保つために真剣に努力しています
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:21.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,その結果 私たちは愛にあふれた\N平和な兄弟関係を楽しんでいます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,サタンはこれからも\N人々を分裂させようとするでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの民のこともです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:33.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,どうすればサタンの攻撃に\N抵抗することができますか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,耳を傾けるべきなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:40.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバが用いている\N「忠実で思慮深い奴隷」の声です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:45.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,世の中ではいろいろなことが\N議論の対象になっていますが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうしたものに\N振り回されないようにしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,王イエス･キリストを支持し
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:55.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,イエスが今用いている\N「忠実で思慮深い奴隷」に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:19:01.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,協力している人全てを エホバは必ず\N祝福してくださることでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:10.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,エホバの証人の世界本部から\NJW Broadcasting®でした
